@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('/Backgroundimages/Chattbild.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            color: aqua; 
        }

        .blurry-background::before {
            content: "";
            display: block;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: -1;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: inherit;
            filter: blur(5px);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="blurry-background">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Welcome to our chat site. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Username, email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Chat Data:</strong> Messages sent and received.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and usage patterns.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve our chat services.</li>
        <li>To ensure the security and integrity of our site.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you regarding updates and support.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
        <li>To protect our rights and safety.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard measures to protect your data from unauthorized access and breaches.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
        <li>Opt-out of communications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Rules for Posting</h2>
    <p>When using our chat services, please adhere to the following rules:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Be respectful and courteous to others.</li>
        <li>Do not post any offensive, abusive, or inappropriate content.</li>
        <li>Any form of harassment, hate speech, or discrimination is strictly prohibited.</li>
        <li>Sharing of personal or sensitive information of others without consent is not allowed.</li>
        <li>Spam, scams, and advertisements are not permitted.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Violation of these rules may result in the removal of your content and, if necessary, suspension or termination of your account.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For any questions or concerns, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@snackis.com">privacy@snackis.com</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
